5:
Listing joys of summer: yukata and...
shaved ice.
7:
Shaved ice determined to be super
yummy. Variety of flavors also
optimal. Strawberry, melon, sweet
red beans and milk...
9:
...In order to complete my mission to
experience the joys of summer, it is
imperative that I try all available
flavo—
23:
I see. So you tended to this little
bird's injuries?
27:
Affirmative. An injury to the wings
was detected, so Nephtim judged
that medical treatment was
necessary.
29:
Stamina confirmed to have
recovered. All administered meals
are eagerly devoured.
33:
...However, flight is not yet possible
without external assistance.
36:
Ah, I getcha. You're using your
powers to give it physical therapy.
50:
Need for elaboration detected. The
bird is a cutie-patootie.
53:
..."The bird" feels too ambiguous.
More specification required.
57:
Assigning new name... From now on,
you will be known as Nem.
61:
Sounds like you two are getting
pretty close.
66:
That makes Nephtim Nem's Keeper.
Ensuring a smooth recovery is now
my responsibility.
73:
Those missions of yours are really
piling up this summer...
75:
But you know... instead of Keeper, I'd
say you're more—
78:
You know what? Never mind. It's just
a word. Do whatever feels right.
82:
Understood. Nephtim will make sure
Nem becomes as fit as a fiddle.
92:
Good job, Nem! Nem is the bestest
bird.
96:
Hey, look at that! Looks like Nem's all
better.
101:
Affirmative. No further injuries
detected. Unassisted flight now
possible. My mission is complete.
104:
But... does that mean Nem can't stay
here anymore?
107: Hm... I wouldn't say that, but...
111:
There is much Nephtim wishes to
teach Nem. Like dancing, playing,
and the joys of summer.
115:
Star power also detected. Nem
could be Nephtim's assistant in
performances!
126:
That's a good question. They might
be searching for Nem as we speak. I
bet Nem misses them too.
138:
Only Nephtim can give orders to
Nem. Therefore...
148:
Nephtim also enjoys flight. Playing
with the others is also fun...
154:
Members of Nem's species not
found. Continuing scan...
157:
Nephtim... What made you decide to
bring Nem back to its family?
178:
Nephtim will no longer give you
orders.
181:
Nephtim has learned much in her
time with Stella and the others.
187:
Please... avoid further injury at all
cost, and... prioritize your health.
192:
...Nem is now fit as a fiddle.
Nephtim's mission is complete.
194:
But why... does Nephtim feel empty
inside?
198:
...Let's head back. It's going to get
dark soon.
